<template>
  <v-card style="width: 1000px" :elevation="12" class="pa-5 rounded-xl">
    <v-card-title class="text-teal-darken-4 text-h4 text-center"
      >Registeration From</v-card-title
    >
    <v-form>
      <v-row>
        <v-col md="6">
          <v-text-field variant="solo-filled" label="Name"></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
        <v-col md="6">
          <v-text-field variant="solo-filled" label="Email"></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
      <v-row>
        <v-col md="6">
          <v-text-field variant="solo-filled" label="Contact"></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
        <v-col md="6">
          <v-select
            variant="solo-filled"
            label="Role"
            items="['Property Owner','Contractor']"
            item-value="[0,1]"
          >
          </v-select>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
      <v-row>
        <v-col md="6">
          <v-text-field
            variant="solo-filled"
            type="password"
            label="Password"
            prepend-inner-icon="mdi-eye"
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
        <v-col md="6">
          <v-text-field
            variant="solo-filled"
            label="Confirm Password"
            type="password"
            prepend-inner-icon="mdi-eye"
          ></v-text-field>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
      <v-row>
        <v-col>
          <v-textarea variant="" label="Address"> </v-textarea>
        </v-col>
      </v-row>
    </v-form>
  </v-card>
</template>
<script setup></script>
<style scoped></style>
